      "title": "Presidential Secretariat back to normal",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The work of the President's Secretariat was suspended due to the agitation for the resignation of former President Gotabaya Rajapaksa.",
        "In this case, the work of the said Secretariat will be resumed after about 100 days."
